syllabus:
本課程的學習目標包含：
(1)塑膠材料的種類、特性、及其應用；
(2)塑膠產品的成形方法；
(3)塑膠射出成形品的設計；
(4)塑膠射出成形機的分類與規格；
(5)塑膠射出成形品的品質；
(6)塑膠射出成形模具的構造；
(7)塑膠射出成形模具零件規格與選用；
(8)塑膠射出成形品的缺陷與對策；
(9)塑膠射出成形模具設計範例；
(10)熱澆道模具；
(11)特殊成形方法。
The learning objectives of this course include:
(1) Types, characteristics, and applications of plastic materials;
(2) Forming methods of plastic products;
(3) Design of plastic injection molded products;
(4) Classification and specifications of plastic injection molding machines;
(5) The quality of plastic injection molded products;
(6) The structure of the plastic injection mold;
(7) Specifications and selection of plastic injection molding mold parts;
(8) Defects and countermeasures of plastic injection molded products;
(9) Plastic injection molding mold design examples.
(10) Hot runner mold
(11) Special forming method.

